"**Unquoted terms:** Search terms that contain non-alphanumeric "
"characters/special characters outside of quotation marks are removed. For"
" example, using ``abcd \"**\" && abc`` as a search term will return "
"results for a search for ``abcd \"**\" abc`` as the ``&&`` characters "
"weren't within the quotation marks."
